<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="with-prep">with <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɪð, wɪθ/    美 /wɪθ, wɪð/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>和...一起：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I still miss the days when she was with us. 
我依然很怀念她和我们在一起的日子。</p><footer> 2010 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>赞同 (某人)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Are you with me or against me? 
你是支持我还是反对我？</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>具有；带有；包含</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a cup with a handle 
有把儿的杯子</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Success is the ability to go from one failure to another with no loss of enthusiasm.
成功是，你即使跨过一个又一个失败，但也没有失去热情。</p><footer>---丘吉尔</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cost 500 dollars with tax
连税在内价格为500美元</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>对于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These topics are very popular with students.
这些话题很受学生欢迎。</p><footer>2012 辽宁改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Be patient with other people. 
对别人要有耐心。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>随着：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>change with the temperature
随温度而变化</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With that last remark, she turned and left. 
说完最后那句话，她便转身离开了。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.★ <strong>由于；因为：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I felt like crying with happiness. 
我高兴得想哭。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>jump with joy
高兴地跳起来</p></div>

<h4 id="7">7.★ <strong>用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cut it with a knife.
用刀把它切开。</p></div>

<h4 id="8">8.★ <strong>以...；带着：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should overcome our weaknesses and fears with courage and determination. 
我们要用勇气与决心来克服自己的弱点与恐惧。</p><footer>2016 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He prepared everything with great care. 
他精心地准备每件事。</p></div>

<p>注: “with＋名词＋不定式 / 动词-ing / 过去分词 / 介词短语等”结构常作状语，表伴随、原因、条 件等，还可作定语。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With no other kids of my age in the neighborhood,I had to spend hours by myself.
由于邻里没有和我同龄的孩子，我不得不一个人打发时间。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With you to help us, we’ll surely succeed. 
有你来帮我们，我们一定会成功。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With prices going up so fast, we can’t afford luxuries.
由于物价猛涨，我们买不起高档商品。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They sat together around the table, with the door shut. 
他们关着门围桌而坐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police kept shouting at the man to come out with his hands up. 
警察一直大声呼喊，让那位男子举起双手出来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The workforce is made up of 400 workers, with most of them women. 
职工一共400人，其中大多数是女性。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The Scottish girl <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ blue eyes won the first prize in the Fifth Chinese Speech Contest.  （2014 陕西改）  </li>
<li>The wine industry in the area has developed in a special way, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_little foreign ownership.   （2009 北京）<br />
A.by <br />
B.of <br />
C.with <br />
D.from  </li>
<li>You have no idea how she finished the relay race <strong><em>_</em></strong>_her foot wounded so much.  （2008 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. with  2. C  3. with  </p></div>